rComments: so amazing. He's teaching at U of Manitoba now (where I took the class). Best teacher i've ever; had cares about his students, so easy to talk to, tells you exactly what he wants in papers. He's a tough grader but just try and you'll do fine. Lectures were unreal - opens up your mind I learnt so much about the world and people.

Really interesting lecturer, definitely cared about his students and the subject matter. Occasionally seemed a little disorganized in the order material was presented, but overall a great experience and a nice guy. Very helpful outside of class.
